<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِجَهَالَةٍ}</span> ... بِسَفَهٍ، وَجَهْلٍ لِعَاقِبَتِهَا، وَكُلُّ مَنْ عَصَى اللهَ فَهُوَ جَاهِلٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُمَّةً}</span> ... إِمَامًا، جَامِعًا لِخِصَالِ الخَيْرِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَانِتًا}</span> ... خَاضِعًا، مُدَاوِمًا عَلَى الطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَنِيفًا}</span> ... مَائِلًا عَنِ الشِّرْكِ إِلَى التَّوْحِيدِ قَصْدًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اجْتَبَاهُ}</span> ... اخْتَارَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلِ رَبِّكَ}</span> ... دِينِ رَبِّكَ، وَطَرِيقِهِ المُسْتَقِيم<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>